description: Merino wool-pile fabric is glued onto a durable hemp backing to create an incredibly soft cushion for your foot.  Wool absorbs 30-40% of its own weight in moisture. Bacteria can only thrive in moisture.  Wool and hemp are naturally bacteria, mold, and fungus resistant.  Neither take on body odors. For uniform work shoes and fitted boots.
